gg_a3p_impact

This is a medium sized Gun Game map inspired by the game A3P. Enjoy!

-	64 Spawns
-	Nav file for bots
-	Overview Radar Map
-	Cube Maps
-	Optimized for better FPS
-	Everything is packaged into the .bsp with Pakrat
-	Soundscapes
-       3d Skybox
-       Buy Zones
-	Custom Textures from [-B-]
-	Custom Skybox Texture from [-B-]
